synatx:
  less [options]  [files]

  less is use to overcome the cat problem 
  large file will not display all content in cat ,u cant scroll all content in cat 
  using less u can naviagte the file content

-------------------------------------
less filename    :will display the contetnt of file is uwant to go down press down arrow for up up arrow
                    use space to navigate page by page
                    for up page use key 'b'
                    to go to end press capital 'G'
                    go to top to press '1g'
                    to serach content in file us ecommand : /searckkey and enter  
                    to search down to up use command : ?book
                    to quit press 'q' key


